民外，所花費的行政費亦少，他舉例關愛基金每人的行政費是5%，而派錢則不足1%。<br />\n</span><br />\n工聯會立法會議員麥美娟澄清，工聯會主張政府有盈餘之下，應該全民派錢，認為有人捏造事實，繼續擴大社會撕裂。陸頌雄稱，希望政府用好財政盈餘，大刀闊斧改善外判制度和整體勞工市場員工待遇，又建議林鄭設立新生嬰兒基金，讓每個嬰兒出生都應該有一封「大利是」，鼓勵生育。<br />\n<br />\n律政司司長鄭若驊其後到場並遭到示威者包圍，有示威者向她撒「回水一萬」紅色溪錢。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T08:12:55.000Z","msg":"又精神分裂"},{"pid":"287c3f95794a7a8edcb67c3c5f65d299952cb18d","tid":581221,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T08:18:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1382316-20180224.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1382316-20180224.htm&d=ZEo7vQ9fCHK54tDwjZR3fcPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=f08f5265\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1382316-20180224.htm&h=8002fb44\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1382316-20180224.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n政府下星期三公布新一份財政預算案，立法會議員朱凱廸在一個電台節目說，現時社會太集中在應否「派錢」及金額水平，忽略了收入，擔心市民會有印象認為「賣地收入高是好事」，強調政府的賣地收入增加，樓價亦會居高不下。他認為，政府現時應考慮如何善用土地資源，建造更多市民可負擔的房屋。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/164126/-%E7%AB%8B%E6%9C%83%E8%A3%9C%E9%81%B8-%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%BF%E8%B2%A1%E7%88%BA%E7%84%A1%E6%B4%BE%E9%8C%A2-%E5%80%A1%E7%8B%97%E5%B9%B4%E6%B4%BE9000-%E5%A8%A5%E5%A7%90-%E6%94%9D%E4%B8%80%E6%94%9D%E5%A4%AA%E6%AD%B2%E5%95%A6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2F164126%2F-%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25A3%259C%25E9%2581%25B8-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25BB%25BF%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E7%2588%25BA%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E9%258C%25A2-%25E5%2580%25A1%25E7%258B%2597%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%25B4%25BE9000-%25E5%25A8%25A5%25E5%25A7%2590-%25E6%2594%259D%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%2594%259D%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%2595%25A6&d=ZEo7vQ9fCHK54tDwjZR3fcPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=5e7ad901\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/164126/-%E7%AB%8B%E6%9C%83%E8%A3%9C%E9%81%B8-%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%BF%E8%B2%A1%E7%88%BA%E7%84%A1%E6%B4%BE%E9%8C%A2-%E5%80%A1%E7%8B%97%E5%B9%B4%E6%B4%BE9000-%E5%A8%A5%E5%A7%90-%E6%94%9D%E4%B8%80%E6%94%9D%E5%A4%AA%E6%AD%B2%E5%95%A6</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180224/s00001/1519435769690\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180224%2Fs00001%2F1519435769690&d=ZEo7vQ9fCHK54tDwjZR3fcPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=53be545a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180224%2Fs00001%2F1519435769690&h=54bc3b9a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180224/s00001/1519435769690</a><br />\n<br />\n梁耀忠今早在商台節目表示，以往街工的原則是不贊成派錢，但早前經調查，發現七成受訪者指政府亂花錢、理財不善，贊成派錢，所以他認為不如把錢派給市民，可以紓緩市民壓力。<br />\n<br />\n同場的張超雄表明不贊成派錢，認為派錢證明政府束手無策和無承擔。他說，政府的整體公共開支偏低，只佔國民生產總值不足兩成。他指日本、英國和歐洲等地的整體公共開支所佔比重遠比香港高。<br />\n<br />\n陳志全在節目上表示贊成派錢，認為「既然政府不肯做，不如還富於民」，又指退稅措施只是「還富於富」。他表示，派錢和將盈餘撥在其他方面，並非二擇其一。<br />\n<br />\n朱凱廸因感冒未能出席節目，陳志全則指朱在原則上不支持派錢，但更反對退稅，如果要選擇一個做法的話就寧願派錢。朱凱廸其後透過電話表示，現時的討論比較集中派錢，忽略了收入方面的討論，他擔心市民會有「賣地收入高是好事」的印象，日後樓價將會居高不下，變相亦是負擔，即使派錢，「日後供樓的錢都喺返度」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180220/20309655\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180220%2F20309655&d=ZEo7vQ9fCHK54tDwjZR3fcPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=b81cf44c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180220%2F20309655&h=9e827e0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180220/20309655</a><br />\n<br />\n公民黨立法會議員郭家麒則表示，按照歐美國家的做法，應該只有在經濟衰退的時候才會選擇「派錢」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1145081/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1145081%2F&d=ZEo7vQ9fCHK54tDwjZR3fcPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=8d754c48\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1145081%2F&h=1f3a3861\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1145081/</a><br />\n<br />\n郭榮鏗梁繼昌反對派錢 邵家臻反對全民派<br />\n<br />\n屆政府首份財政預算案將於下星期發表，專業議政4名議員對政府在庫房大量盈餘下是否派錢意見不一。<br />\n<br />\n法律界郭榮鏗及會計界梁繼昌都反對派錢，認為是短視做法，行政費用高，負責任政府應該有願景，將盈餘用得其所用在醫療、教育及福利等方面。<br />\n<br />\n教育界葉建源就希望，BCA、即改革後的TSA農曆新年有好消息。認為如果政府做好長遠規劃，各種政策都得到社會支持後，直接派錢是可行的方法。<br />\n<br />\n社會福利界邵家臻建議，向65歲以上長者，每月直接派發3500元，及將盈餘投放在民間社會發展基金及關愛基金作融資安排，更較一次過派錢有效。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2015015/%E5%BB%BA%E5%88%B6%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E6%B3%9B%E6%B0%91%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97%E6%A1%88%E6%B4%BE%E9%8C%A2%E3%80%80%E8%A7%92%E8%89%B2%E8%AA%BF%E6%8F%9B%EF%BC%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2015015%2F%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%2588%25B6%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581%25E6%25B3%259B%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25B0%258D%25E9%25A0%2590%25E7%25AE%2597%25E6%25A1%2588%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E9%258C%25A2%25E3%2580%2580%25E8%25A7%2592%25E8%2589%25B2%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%258F%259B%25EF%25BC%259F&d=ZEo7vQ9fCHK54tDwjZR3fcPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=be5bae3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2015015/%E5%BB%BA%E5%88%B6%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E6%B3%9B%E6%B0%91%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97%E6%A1%88%E6%B4%BE%E9%8C%A2%E3%80%80%E8%A7%92%E8%89%B2%E8%AA%BF%E6%8F%9B%EF%BC%9F</a>"},{"pid":"9599a4ea3821213f2e6501a861842eb3cee12bfa","tid":581221,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T08:18:42.000Z","msg":"仲有販民派會議召集人莫乃光呀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180208/20298766\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180208%2F20298766&d=ZEo7vQ9fCHK54tDwjZR3fcPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=d03c4a30\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180208%2F20298766&h=15e56b8a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180208/20298766</a><br />\n<br />\n民主派會議召集人莫乃光表示，希望政府善用龐大財政盈餘作長遠發展，而非集中於一次性派糖"},{"pid":"2da9a96208b3d442634e68057f69ee0141da7ab7","tid":581221,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T08:19:20.000Z","msg":"泛民點解又想呃人"},{"pid":"88b495a0e79fd245eb75e8886d0a67f3a5a3d416","tid":581221,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T08:20:26.000Z","msg":"紅字又點<br />\n咁就想呃9人"},{"pid":"6bb5a4340bfb5ea5ece778e821a2023339aa95ba","tid":581221,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T08:22:35.000Z","msg":"公布之前就得陳志全支持<br />\n另外個班就一係反對一係連講支持都唔柒敢呀"},{"pid":"7849a506b4530234070fe8380a632d8008b2e83f","tid":581221,"uid":6604,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dd7fb1052294466fe52586c93c86c56105347c04","tid":581221,"uid":51183,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T08:10:51.000Z","msg":"長毛係咪泛民先<br />\n佢N年前已經話回水一萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T08:22:39.000Z","msg":"其實泛民山頭林立<br />\n是但將一條戇鳩講嘅嘢就當晒係成個泛民講<br />\n<br />\n割包皮反對派錢，但佢嘅原因如下 :<br />\n<br />\n公民黨立法會議員郭家麒表示，不贊成預算案向每名市民「派錢」。他出席本台節目時表示，按照一般歐美國家的做法，只有在經濟衰退時才應該「派錢」，以鼓勵市民消費，刺激經濟增長。<span style=\"color: red;\">現時公共開支不能超過本地生產總值20%的限制，他形容是一個「金剛箍」，不利於制定完善的公共財政政策，政府應該作出長遠財政規劃，例如增加醫療開支等。<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1381489-20180219.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1381489-20180219.htm&d=ZEo7vQ9fCHK54tDwjZR3fcPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=1139e759\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1381489-20180219.htm&h=f99c3fe9\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1381489-20180219.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n唔派錢，但佢建議要增加醫療<br />\n其實冇語啱定錯<br />\n喺佢個角度<br />\n派左錢，市民健康唔會因而改善<br />\n反而投放醫療,長遠可能仲好<br />\n<br />\n記得楊永強主政年代，香港公立醫院服務水平係拍得住私家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0adcf462dbb169415dde2626d07381345459c90","tid":581221,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6bb5a4340bfb5ea5ece778e821a2023339aa95ba","tid":581221,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T08:22:35.000Z","msg":"公布之前就得陳志全支持<br />\n另外個班就一係反對一係連講支持都唔柒敢呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T08:24:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">公布之前係工賊會, 民賤聯話支持<br />\n連廿蚊張都支持架</span></span>"},{"pid":"f5a04ae89b53b6a4eea95828414afc5f9cabd95a","tid":581221,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7849a506b4530234070fe8380a632d8008b2e83f","tid":581221,"uid":6604,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dd7fb1052294466fe52586c93c86c56105347c04","tid":581221,"uid":51183,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T08:10:51.000Z","msg":"長毛係咪泛民先<br />\n佢N年前已經話回水一萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T08:22:39.000Z","msg":"其實泛民山頭林立<br />\n是但將一條戇鳩講嘅嘢就當晒係成個泛民講<br />\n<br />\n割包皮反對派錢，但佢嘅原因如下 :<br />\n<br />\n公民黨立法會議員郭家麒表示，不贊成預算案向每名市民「派錢」。他出席本台節目時表示，按照一般歐美國家的做法，只有在經濟衰退時才應該「派錢」，以鼓勵市民消費，刺激經濟增長。<span style=\"color: red;\">現時公共開支不能超過本地生產總值20%的限制，他形容是一個「金剛箍」，不利於制定完善的公共財政政策，政府應該作出長遠財政規劃，例如增加醫療開支等。<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1381489-20180219.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1381489-20180219.htm&d=ZEo7vQ9fCHK54tDwjZR3fcPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=1139e759\" data-ef-url=\"https://emb